data.description: Discover the charm of this stunning 5-bedroom, 3-bathroom home! Recently upgraded with a new roof, AC, and impact windows throughout, this property boasts modern amenities and stylish finishes. The bathrooms and kitchen have been tastefully remodeled, providing a contemporary and inviting atmosphere. Each spacious bedroom easily accommodates a king-size bed, making it ideal for your large family.    Perfect for both homeowners and savvy investors, this property allows for flexible usage. Consider renting a portion while enjoying the comfort of the main living space. With FHA, VA, and conventional loan options available, this is truly a first-time homebuyer's dream.
